OL,3,CStarmer shares pride in England team
OL,4,Cafter win over France seals third
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer congratulated
OL,7,FEngland's footballers after they
OL,8,Fwrapped up their World Cup campaign
OL,9,Fand his time as Prime Minister with a
OL,10,Fthrilling 6-4 victory over France.
OL,12,FBukayo Saka scored a hat-trick with
OL,13,FEzri Konsa and Jude Bellingham also on
OL,14,Ftarget as England bounced back from
OL,15,Ftheir disappointment in losing to
OL,16,FArgentina in the semi-final to clinch
OL,17,Fthird place ` their best World Cup
OL,18,Ffinish outside winning the tournament
OL,19,Fin 1966.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
