OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784429266
OL,3,CStarmer shares pride in England team
OL,4,Cafter win over France seals third
OL,6,FKylian Mbappe scored twice for France
OL,7,Fin Miami as they threatened to wipe
OL,8,Fout a 4-0 half-time deficit, moving
OL,9,Fahead of Lionel Messi to become the
OL,10,Ftop scorer in the tournament and in
OL,11,FWorld Cup history with 22 goals.
OL,13,FSir Keir, who will be replaced as
OL,14,FPrime Minister by Andy Burnham on
OL,15,FMonday, posted on X: "Great result
OL,16,Ftonight @England. You've done us
OL,17,Fproud."
OL,26,@wD@VOUyD@GO]
