OL,3,CStarmer shares pride in England team
OL,4,Cafter win over France seals third
OL,6,FFormer England captain Sir David
OL,7,FBeckham sent his congratulations in a
OL,8,Fseries of posts on Instagram, saying:
OL,9,F"Great way to end the tournament
OL,10,F@England."
OL,12,FHe also posted images of "hat-trick
OL,13,Fhero" Saka and Bellingham, who wrapped
OL,14,Fup the victory with an individual
OL,15,Feffort in the dying seconds.
OL,17,FBellingham's seventh goal of the
OL,18,Ftournament made him England's highest
OL,19,Fscorer in a single tournament.
