OL,3,CStarmer shares pride in England team
OL,4,Cafter win over France seals third
OL,6,FGoverning body Fifa also congratulated
OL,7,FEngland, posting a picture of the
OL,8,Fsquad on the Instagram after they were
OL,9,Fpresented with their bronze medals
OL,10,Fwith the message: "Congratulations to
OL,11,F@England, third place at @FIFAWorldCup
OL,12,F2026!
OL,14,F"Their best finish since winning the
OL,15,Ftournament in 1966."
